💸 FinFlow Pro — Smart Finance Dashboard

A modern, feature-rich personal finance management web app that helps users track income, expenses, budgets, and financial insights with an intuitive UI.

🚀 Features
🔐 Authentication
Demo login system (Admin & Viewer roles)
Role-based UI access
Session persistence using localStorage
📊 Dashboard Overview
Total Balance, Income, Expenses, Savings Rate
Month-over-Month comparison
Smart financial insights
💳 Transactions Management
Add / Edit / Delete transactions
Filter by:
Date range
Category
Type (Income / Expense)
Search keywords
Pagination support
📈 Data Visualization
Balance trend charts
Category-wise expense breakdown
Monthly analytics
💡 Smart Insights
Budget overuse alerts
Spending trend analysis
Savings performance tracking
🎯 Budget Management
Set category-wise budgets
Track overspending
Alerts for threshold limits
🔁 Recurring Transactions
Identify recurring income/expenses
Auto insights generation
🌍 Multi-Currency Support
INR, USD, EUR, GBP
Real-time conversion logic
🌙 Dark Mode
Toggle between light & dark themes
Persistent theme settings
📤 Export Options
Export data as:
CSV
JSON
PDF reports
🛠️ Tech Stack
Frontend: HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript (Vanilla)
Styling: Custom CSS with modern UI design
State Management: JavaScript objects
Storage: Browser LocalStorage
Charts: Canvas-based rendering
Deployment: GitHub Pages CI/CD
📂 Project Structure
📁 FinFlow-Pro
│── index.html      # Main UI structure
│── style.css       # Styling and themes
│── app.js          # Core logic & features
│── deploy.yml      # GitHub Pages deployment workflow
